parts.text:
```json
{
"application": "SLURM",
"other_software": "mpiexec",
"resource_requirements": {
"nodes": "variable, specified in case file",
"processors_per_node": "variable, specified in case file",
"wall_clock_time": "variable, specified in case file",
"memory": "not specified",
"storage": "not specified"
},
"input_file": {
"format": "case_file",
"structure": [
"case_name",
"ALGO_MODE (1-Gauss-Seidel, 2-Jacobi)",
"TERM_MODE (1-Precision, 2-Iteration)",
"termination value (precision or iteration)",
"BDY_FUNC (1-0/linear, 2-sinusodial)",
"number of samples",
"wall clock time",
"list of configurations (K-P-N, K: number of nodes, P: number of processors, N: number of interlines)"
],
"separator": ":"
},
"output_files": [
"{JOB_SCRIPT_NAME}.job",
"{JOB_SCRIPT_NAME}.err",
"{JOB_SCRIPT_NAME}.out"
]
}
```
